stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> OpenDashboard
    OpenDashboard --> ConnectWebSocket : ws://host/ws/alerts/
    ConnectWebSocket --> Listening
    Listening --> AlertReceived : New alert broadcast
    AlertReceived --> UpdateLiveFeed
    UpdateLiveFeed --> ShowNotification
    ShowNotification --> Listening
    Listening --> ConnectionLost : Network error
    ConnectionLost --> Reconnecting : Auto-reconnect
    Reconnecting --> Listening : Reconnected
    Listening --> UserLeaves : Navigate away
    UserLeaves --> Disconnect
    Disconnect --> [*]